author: julianfoad
msg: Bash-completion: update the list of commands, and don't output redundant
Remove obsolete commands (get).  Add new commands (annotate, ann, pd).
Remove redundant (unambiguous) abbreviations, so that (e.g.) expanding "st"
gives "status" instead of giving the choices "st stat status".
Restore alphabetical order in the lists.

author: philip
msg: Arrange for nodes returned from the fs node cache to have a
defined lifetime.  This fixes at least one "non-existent node"
(dag_node_cache_get): Add a pool parameter.  Call svn_fs__dag_dup
and return the duplicate node rather than the cached node.
(open_path, get_dag): Pass the trail pool to dag_node_cache_get.
